						 <p>This is an *amazing* first SCP, and it's definitely one of my favorite Internet-based ones. A strong +1</p> <div class="collapsible-block"> <div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">SPOILERS</a></div> <div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none"> <div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">SPOILERS</a></div> <div class="collapsible-block-content"> <p>What's the audio in the final entry saying? I can hear &quot;It's okay,&quot; but she says something after that that I can't make out.</p> </div> </div> </div> 
				 	]]>
