						 <p>My first SCP.</p> <p>Many thanks to my reviewers and greenlighters: <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/drakimoto" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=5255688&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1571611816" alt="DrAkimoto" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=5255688)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/drakimoto" >DrAkimoto</a></span> (twice!), <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/rockteethmotheyes" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4022320&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1571611816" alt="RockTeethMothEyes" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4022320)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/rockteethmotheyes" >RockTeethMothEyes</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/dyslexion" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=5549954&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1571611816" alt="Dyslexion" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=5549954)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/dyslexion" >Dyslexion</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/cybersqyd" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=5336470&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1571611816" alt="cybersqyd" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=5336470)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/cybersqyd" >cybersqyd</a></span> (idea), <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/simartar" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=5489226&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1571611816" alt="Simartar" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=5489226)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/simartar" >Simartar</a></span> (idea)</p> <div class="collapsible-block"> <div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">Other&nbsp;credits</a></div> <div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none"> <div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">Other&nbsp;credits</a></div> <div class="collapsible-block-content"> <p>Photos:</p> <ul> <li><a href="https://ccsearch.creativecommons.org/photos/af75e195-984d-4671-b86a-dfe7e16328fa">https://ccsearch.creativecommons.org/photos/af75e195-984d-4671-b86a-dfe7e16328fa</a></li> <li><a href="https://ccsearch.creativecommons.org/photos/4a7d4ada-5e15-4146-b812-3872a5f003b0">https://ccsearch.creativecommons.org/photos/4a7d4ada-5e15-4146-b812-3872a5f003b0</a></li> <li><a href="https://ccsearch.creativecommons.org/photos/150b5ddd-34a7-4944-80dd-055736b281bf">https://ccsearch.creativecommons.org/photos/150b5ddd-34a7-4944-80dd-055736b281bf</a></li> </ul> <p>There is some <em>Moby Dick</em> wedged into SCP-4361-AV-1.</p> <p>Plus a very special thanks to my wife for her two seconds of voice-over.</p> </div> </div> </div> 
				 	]]>
